% Chapter 11 -- a first picture.
%
% Open a 200x150 offscreen surface, fill it with a red rectangle,
% write the result as a PNG.
%
% Output:
%   /tmp/sli3-ch11-01-rect.png  (PNG, 200x150)

200 150 newoffscreen pop
1 0 0 setrgbcolor
20 20 160 110 rect fill
(/tmp/sli3-ch11-01-rect.png) currentpage writepng
currentpage closepage
quit
